{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I grew up in New York City,"},{"time":3000,"text":"between Harlem and the Bronx."},{"time":5000,"text":"Growing up as a boy, we were taught"},{"time":7000,"text":"that men had to be tough, had to be strong,"},{"time":9000,"text":"had to be courageous, dominating --"},{"time":12000,"text":"no pain, no emotions,"},{"time":14000,"text":"with the exception of anger --"},{"time":16000,"text":"and definitely no fear;"},{"time":18000,"text":"that men are in charge,"},{"time":20000,"text":"which means women are not;"},{"time":22000,"text":"that men lead,"},{"time":24000,"text":"and you should just follow and do what we say;"},{"time":27000,"text":"that men are superior; women are inferior;"},{"time":30000,"text":"that men are strong; women are weak;"},{"time":33000,"text":"that women are of less value,"},{"time":36000,"text":"property of men,"},{"time":38000,"text":"and objects,"},{"time":40000,"text":"particularly sexual objects."},{"time":43000,"text":"I've later come to know that to be"},{"time":46000,"text":"the collective socialization of men,"},{"time":49000,"text":"better known"},{"time":51000,"text":"as the \"man box.\""},{"time":53000,"text":"See this man box has in it"},{"time":55000,"text":"all the ingredients"},{"time":57000,"text":"of how we define what it means to be a man."},{"time":59000,"text":"Now I also want to say, without a doubt,"},{"time":61000,"text":"there are some wonderful, wonderful,"},{"time":63000,"text":"absolutely wonderful things"},{"time":65000,"text":"about being a man."},{"time":67000,"text":"But at the same time,"},{"time":69000,"text":"there's some stuff"},{"time":71000,"text":"that's just straight up twisted,"},{"time":73000,"text":"and we really need to begin"},{"time":75000,"text":"to challenge, look at it"},{"time":77000,"text":"and really get in the process"},{"time":79000,"text":"of deconstructing, redefining,"},{"time":82000,"text":"what we come to know as manhood."}]},{"cues":[{"time":86000,"text":"This is my two at home, Kendall and Jay."},{"time":88000,"text":"They're 11 and 12."},{"time":90000,"text":"Kendall's 15 months older than Jay."},{"time":92000,"text":"There was a period of time when my wife -- her name is Tammie -- and I,"},{"time":95000,"text":"we just got real busy and whip, bam, boom:"},{"time":97000,"text":"Kendall and Jay."},{"time":99000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":101000,"text":"And when they were about five and six,"},{"time":103000,"text":"four and five,"},{"time":105000,"text":"Jay could come to me,"},{"time":107000,"text":"come to me crying."},{"time":109000,"text":"It didn't matter what she was crying about,"},{"time":111000,"text":"she could get on my knee, she could snot my sleeve up,"},{"time":113000,"text":"just cry, cry it out."},{"time":115000,"text":"Daddy's got you. That's all that's important."}]},{"cues":[{"time":118000,"text":"Now Kendall on the other hand --"},{"time":120000,"text":"and like I said, he's only 15 months older than her --"},{"time":123000,"text":"he'd come to me crying,"},{"time":125000,"text":"it's like as soon as I would hear him cry,"},{"time":127000,"text":"a clock would go off."},{"time":129000,"text":"I would give the boy probably about 30 seconds,"},{"time":132000,"text":"which means, by the time he got to me,"},{"time":135000,"text":"I was already saying things like, \"Why are you crying?"},{"time":137000,"text":"Hold your head up. Look at me."},{"time":140000,"text":"Explain to me what's wrong."},{"time":142000,"text":"Tell me what's wrong. I can't understand you."},{"time":144000,"text":"Why are you crying?\""},{"time":146000,"text":"And out of my own frustration"},{"time":148000,"text":"of my role and responsibility"},{"time":150000,"text":"of building him up as a man"},{"time":152000,"text":"to fit into these guidelines"},{"time":154000,"text":"and these structures that are defining this man box,"},{"time":157000,"text":"I would find myself saying things like,"},{"time":159000,"text":"\"Just go in your room."},{"time":161000,"text":"Just go on, go on in your room."},{"time":163000,"text":"Sit down,"},{"time":165000,"text":"get yourself together"},{"time":167000,"text":"and come back and talk to me"},{"time":169000,"text":"when you can talk to me like a --\" what?"},{"time":171000,"text":"(Audience: Man.)"},{"time":173000,"text":"Like a man."},{"time":175000,"text":"And he's five years old."},{"time":177000,"text":"And as I grow in life,"},{"time":179000,"text":"I would say to myself,"},{"time":181000,"text":"\"My God, what's wrong with me?"},{"time":183000,"text":"What am I doing? Why would I do this?\""},{"time":186000,"text":"And I think back."},{"time":188000,"text":"I think back to my father."}]},{"cues":[{"time":191000,"text":"There was a time in my life"},{"time":193000,"text":"where we had a very troubled experience in our family."},{"time":196000,"text":"My brother, Henry, he died tragically"},{"time":198000,"text":"when we were teenagers."},{"time":200000,"text":"We lived in New York City, as I said."},{"time":202000,"text":"We lived in the Bronx at the time,"},{"time":205000,"text":"and the burial was in a place called Long Island,"},{"time":208000,"text":"it was about two hours outside of the city."},{"time":211000,"text":"And as we were preparing"},{"time":213000,"text":"to come back from the burial,"},{"time":215000,"text":"the cars stopped at the bathroom"},{"time":217000,"text":"to let folks take care of themselves"},{"time":219000,"text":"before the long ride back to the city."},{"time":221000,"text":"And the limousine empties out."},{"time":223000,"text":"My mother, my sister, my auntie, they all get out,"},{"time":225000,"text":"but my father and I stayed in the limousine,"},{"time":228000,"text":"and no sooner than the women got out,"},{"time":231000,"text":"he burst out crying."},{"time":234000,"text":"He didn't want cry in front of me,"},{"time":236000,"text":"but he knew he wasn't going to make it back to the city,"},{"time":239000,"text":"and it was better me than to allow himself"},{"time":241000,"text":"to express these feelings and emotions in front of the women."},{"time":244000,"text":"And this is a man"},{"time":246000,"text":"who, 10 minutes ago,"},{"time":248000,"text":"had just put his teenage son"},{"time":250000,"text":"in the ground --"},{"time":252000,"text":"something I just can't even imagine."},{"time":257000,"text":"The thing that sticks with me the most"},{"time":259000,"text":"is that he was apologizing to me"},{"time":262000,"text":"for crying in front of me,"},{"time":264000,"text":"and at the same time, he was also giving me props,"},{"time":267000,"text":"lifting me up,"},{"time":269000,"text":"for not crying."}]},{"cues":[{"time":271000,"text":"I come to also look at this"},{"time":274000,"text":"as this fear that we have as men,"},{"time":276000,"text":"this fear that just has us paralyzed,"},{"time":278000,"text":"holding us hostage"},{"time":280000,"text":"to this man box."},{"time":282000,"text":"I can remember speaking"},{"time":284000,"text":"to a 12-year-old boy, a football player,"},{"time":286000,"text":"and I asked him, I said,"},{"time":288000,"text":"\"How would you feel if,"},{"time":290000,"text":"in front of all the players,"},{"time":292000,"text":"your coach told you you were playing like a girl?\""},{"time":295000,"text":"Now I expected him to say something like,"},{"time":297000,"text":"I'd be sad; I'd be mad; I'd be angry, or something like that."},{"time":299000,"text":"No, the boy said to me --"},{"time":301000,"text":"the boy said to me,"},{"time":303000,"text":"\"It would destroy me.\""},{"time":306000,"text":"And I said to myself,"},{"time":309000,"text":"\"God, if it would destroy him"},{"time":311000,"text":"to be called a girl,"},{"time":313000,"text":"what are we then teaching him"},{"time":316000,"text":"about girls?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":319000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":323000,"text":"It took me back to a time"},{"time":325000,"text":"when I was about 12 years old."},{"time":328000,"text":"I grew up in tenement buildings in the inner city."},{"time":331000,"text":"At this time we're living in the Bronx,"},{"time":333000,"text":"and in the building next to where I lived there was a guy named Johnny."},{"time":336000,"text":"He was about 16 years old,"},{"time":338000,"text":"and we were all about 12 years old -- younger guys."},{"time":340000,"text":"And he was hanging out with all us younger guys."},{"time":342000,"text":"And this guy, he was up to a lot of no good."},{"time":344000,"text":"He was the kind of kid who parents would have to wonder,"},{"time":346000,"text":"\"What is this 16-year-old boy doing with these 12-year-old boys?\""},{"time":349000,"text":"And he did spend a lot of time up to no good."},{"time":351000,"text":"He was a troubled kid."},{"time":353000,"text":"His mother had died from a heroin overdose."},{"time":355000,"text":"He was being raised by his grandmother."},{"time":357000,"text":"His father wasn't on the set."},{"time":359000,"text":"His grandmother had two jobs."},{"time":361000,"text":"He was home alone a lot."},{"time":363000,"text":"But I've got to tell you, we young guys,"},{"time":365000,"text":"we looked up to this dude, man."},{"time":367000,"text":"He was cool. He was fine."},{"time":370000,"text":"That's what the sisters said, \"He was fine.\""},{"time":373000,"text":"He was having sex."},{"time":375000,"text":"We all looked up to him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":377000,"text":"So one day, I'm out in front of the house doing something --"},{"time":379000,"text":"just playing around, doing something -- I don't know what."},{"time":382000,"text":"He looks out his window; he calls me upstairs; he said, \"Hey Anthony.\""},{"time":384000,"text":"They called me Anthony growing up as a kid."},{"time":386000,"text":"\"Hey Anthony, come on upstairs.\""},{"time":388000,"text":"Johnny call, you go."},{"time":390000,"text":"So I run right upstairs."},{"time":392000,"text":"As he opens the door, he says to me, \"Do you want some?\""},{"time":395000,"text":"Now I immediately knew what he meant."},{"time":397000,"text":"Because for me growing up at that time,"},{"time":399000,"text":"and our relationship with this man box,"},{"time":401000,"text":"\"Do you want some?\" meant one of two things:"},{"time":403000,"text":"sex or drugs --"},{"time":405000,"text":"and we weren't doing drugs."},{"time":407000,"text":"Now my box, my card,"},{"time":409000,"text":"my man box card,"},{"time":411000,"text":"was immediately in jeopardy."},{"time":413000,"text":"Two things: One, I never had sex."},{"time":416000,"text":"We don't talk about that as men."},{"time":418000,"text":"You only tell your dearest, closest friend, sworn to secrecy for life,"},{"time":421000,"text":"the first time you had sex."},{"time":423000,"text":"For everybody else, we go around like we've been having sex since we were two."},{"time":426000,"text":"There ain't no first time."},{"time":428000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":431000,"text":"The other thing I couldn't tell him is that I didn't want any."},{"time":433000,"text":"That's even worse. We're supposed to always be on the prowl."},{"time":436000,"text":"Women are objects,"},{"time":438000,"text":"especially sexual objects."}]},{"cues":[{"time":440000,"text":"Anyway, so I couldn't tell him any of that."},{"time":442000,"text":"So, like my mother would say, make a long story short,"},{"time":444000,"text":"I just simply said to Johnny, \"Yes.\""},{"time":446000,"text":"He told me to go in his room."},{"time":448000,"text":"I go in his room. On his bed is a girl from the neighborhood named Sheila."},{"time":451000,"text":"She's 16 years old."},{"time":453000,"text":"She's nude."},{"time":455000,"text":"She's what I know today to be mentally ill,"},{"time":457000,"text":"higher-functioning at times than others."},{"time":460000,"text":"We had a whole choice of inappropriate names for her."},{"time":464000,"text":"Anyway, Johnny had just gotten through having sex with her."},{"time":467000,"text":"Well actually, he raped her, but he would say he had sex with her."},{"time":470000,"text":"Because, while Sheila never said no,"},{"time":473000,"text":"she also never said yes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":475000,"text":"So he was offering me the opportunity to do the same."},{"time":477000,"text":"So when I go in the room, I close the door."},{"time":480000,"text":"Folks, I'm petrified."},{"time":482000,"text":"I stand with my back to the door so Johnny can't bust in the room"},{"time":484000,"text":"and see that I'm not doing anything,"},{"time":486000,"text":"and I stand there long enough that I could have actually done something."},{"time":489000,"text":"So now I'm no longer trying to figure out what I'm going to do;"},{"time":491000,"text":"I'm trying to figure out how I'm going to get out of this room."},{"time":494000,"text":"So in my 12 years of wisdom,"},{"time":496000,"text":"I zip my pants down,"},{"time":498000,"text":"I walk out into the room,"},{"time":500000,"text":"and lo and behold to me,"},{"time":502000,"text":"while I was in the room with Sheila,"},{"time":504000,"text":"Johnny was back at the window calling guys up."},{"time":507000,"text":"So now there's a living room full of guys."},{"time":509000,"text":"It was like the waiting room in the doctor's office."},{"time":512000,"text":"And they asked me how was it,"},{"time":514000,"text":"and I say to them, \"It was good,\""},{"time":517000,"text":"and I zip my pants up in front of them,"},{"time":519000,"text":"and I head for the door."}]},{"cues":[{"time":521000,"text":"Now I say this all with remorse,"},{"time":523000,"text":"and I was feeling a tremendous amount of remorse at that time,"},{"time":525000,"text":"but I was conflicted, because, while I was feeling remorse, I was excited,"},{"time":528000,"text":"because I didn't get caught."},{"time":530000,"text":"But I knew I felt bad about what was happening."},{"time":532000,"text":"This fear, getting outside the man box,"},{"time":535000,"text":"totally enveloped me."},{"time":537000,"text":"It was way more important to me,"},{"time":539000,"text":"about me and my man box card"},{"time":542000,"text":"than about Sheila"},{"time":544000,"text":"and what was happening to her."}]},{"cues":[{"time":546000,"text":"See collectively, we as men"},{"time":548000,"text":"are taught to have less value in women,"},{"time":550000,"text":"to view them as property and the objects of men."},{"time":553000,"text":"We see that as an equation that equals violence against women."},{"time":556000,"text":"We as men, good men,"},{"time":558000,"text":"the large majority of men,"},{"time":560000,"text":"we operate on the foundation"},{"time":562000,"text":"of this whole collective socialization."},{"time":564000,"text":"We kind of see ourselves separate, but we're very much a part of it."},{"time":567000,"text":"You see, we have to come to understand"},{"time":570000,"text":"that less value, property and objectification is the foundation"},{"time":573000,"text":"and the violence can't happen without it."},{"time":575000,"text":"So we're very much a part of the solution"},{"time":578000,"text":"as well as the problem."},{"time":580000,"text":"The center for disease control says"},{"time":582000,"text":"that men's violence against women is at epidemic proportions,"},{"time":585000,"text":"is the number one health concern for women"},{"time":587000,"text":"in this country and abroad."}]},{"cues":[{"time":589000,"text":"So quickly, I'd like to just say,"},{"time":592000,"text":"this is the love of my life, my daughter Jay."},{"time":595000,"text":"The world I envision for her --"},{"time":597000,"text":"how do I want men to be acting and behaving?"},{"time":599000,"text":"I need you on board. I need you with me."},{"time":601000,"text":"I need you working with me and me working with you"},{"time":604000,"text":"on how we raise our sons"},{"time":606000,"text":"and teach them to be men --"},{"time":608000,"text":"that it's okay to not be dominating,"},{"time":610000,"text":"that it's okay to have feelings and emotions,"},{"time":613000,"text":"that it's okay to promote equality,"},{"time":615000,"text":"that it's okay to have women who are just friends and that's it,"},{"time":618000,"text":"that it's okay to be whole,"},{"time":620000,"text":"that my liberation as a man"},{"time":623000,"text":"is tied to your liberation as a woman. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":626000,"text":"I remember asking a nine-year-old boy,"},{"time":629000,"text":"I asked a nine-year-old boy,"},{"time":632000,"text":"\"What would life be like for you,"},{"time":634000,"text":"if you didn't have to adhere to this man box?\""},{"time":636000,"text":"He said to me, \"I would be free.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":638000,"text":"Thank you folks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":640000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}